Text: Outstanding CandidateI graduated with my MBA in from UT and am participating in the Graduate Business Network prospective student recruiting effort I currently work at Enron Corporation in Houston A fellow colleague of mine at Enron has applied for the fulltime MBA program for Fall The applicants name is Ben Rogers and I believe that he would be an outstanding contribution to the program He is very well respected at Enron from a commercial perspective as well as analytically He is planning to be in Austin on February to attend the QA session and will also be meeting with several professors I think that it would also be helpful for him to meet with you or another member of the admissions committee In case you need to contact Ben directly his office phone number is and email is Let me know if I can be of further assistance Thank you Paul Burkhart Get Your Private Free Email at
